channel.title: Gates are helmets
channel.description: Hey guys. I am relatively new to making servers. But i have stumbled across a flaw in my client.it is delta (inb4 delta sucks) I have been working on this client for the past few days and i really don't want to start looking for another. Here: [url=http://www.freeimagehosting.net/6080a][img]http://www.freeimagehosting.net/t/6080a.jpg[/img][/url] It appears all of my gates on tutorial island appear as fighter hats or whatever they're called from the barbarian minigame. Im sure its a simple solution like missing models or something, so if you could just redirect me to a fix i would appreciate it. thanks in advance _vincent
